Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,《比利小子》前情提要\N{\rYUANWEN}Previously on Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:20.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你为什么对我女儿\N{\rYUANWEN}Why are you interested
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,感兴趣 邦尼先生\N{\rYUANWEN}in my daughter, Mr. Bonney?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:24.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我爱她 我想娶她\N{\rYUANWEN}I love her. I wanna marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:27.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的祖先绝不会同意\N{\rYUANWEN}My ancestors would never approve of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为这应该让你女儿选择\N{\rYUANWEN}I think your daughter deserves that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:32.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦对浩世集团的\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Catron is deeply concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:34.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,财政状况深表关切\N{\rYUANWEN}about the current financial position of the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们知道浩世在赔钱\N{\rYUANWEN}We know that the House is losing money
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们知道英国人汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}and we know the Englishman Tunstall's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要来瓜分我们的市场\N{\rYUANWEN}coming to some of our markets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:41.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道汤斯顿在迪克·布鲁尔的农场\N{\rYUANWEN}I know Tunstall keeps some of his stock
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,养了一批牲畜 牛和马\N{\rYUANWEN}down at Dick Brewer's ranch. His cattle and his horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:45.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我提议来场突袭\N{\rYUANWEN}I say we raid'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:48.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿 给我滚出去 该死的小偷\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey! Get off my property, you damn thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认出了杰西·埃文斯\N{\rYUANWEN}I recognized Jesse Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-驾  -我怀疑\N{\rYUANWEN}- Hiya! - And I suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:56.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,其他人都是七河帮的成员\N{\rYUANWEN}the rest were a part of his 7 Rivers Gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为副警长 我有权要求你\N{\rYUANWEN}And as Deputy Sheriff, I have the authority
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:01:00.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,成立一支武装队\N{\rYUANWEN}to insist that you organize a posse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:01.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,追回所盗赃物\N{\rYUANWEN}and go and recover the stolen goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:04.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走吧 快点\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:10.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,出来吧 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Come out, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-把手举起来  -别开枪\N{\rYUANWEN}Keep your hands up. - Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:16.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,送到天花病房\N{\rYUANWEN}Smallpox ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:22.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们会以公平的价格\N{\rYUANWEN}We'll give you a fair price for your stock,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:24.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,交换你的畜群和不动产\N{\rYUANWEN}your herds and your real estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:26.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为回报呢\N{\rYUANWEN}And in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:28.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你遣散你的员工\N{\rYUANWEN}You get rid of your employees,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,离开林肯县\N{\rYUANWEN}and you leave Lincoln County.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:32.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要是我拒绝你的提议呢\N{\rYUANWEN}And what if I refuse your offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:33.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你会完蛋的\N{\rYUANWEN}You'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有个计划\N{\rYUANWEN}I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:39.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帮杰西和他的人越狱是其中一步\N{\rYUANWEN}It involves helping Jesse and his gang escape from jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:41.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么 我们为什么要这么做\N{\rYUANWEN}What? Why would we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我给了你机会重写人生比利\N{\rYUANWEN}I have given you a second chance in life, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望你用忠诚回报我\N{\rYUANWEN}In return, I expect your loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:49.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,埃文斯先生约翰·汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Evans. John Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就当这是求和礼物吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Think of it as a, uh, a peace offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不许动\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,干得好 比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}Nice work, Billy boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you. -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:02.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我强迫你接受我的昏庸之举\N{\rYUANWEN}By forcing you to go along with my stupid plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,差点害死你\N{\rYUANWEN}I nearly got you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿 把手放在桌子上 新朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey. Hands on the table please, new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你深知有危险\N{\rYUANWEN}You were prepared to stand up for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:09.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你深知有危险\N{\rYUANWEN}You were prepared to stand up for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,依然愿意为我奋不顾身\N{\rYUANWEN}even though you knew the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你到底在干什么 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}What the hell are you doin', Jesse?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿真傻 这里永无和平的可能\N{\rYUANWEN}Tunstall's a fool. There ain't no chance at peace here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:18.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你想要我做搭档\N{\rYUANWEN}If you want me to be a partner in this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你想取得胜利 就得相信我\N{\rYUANWEN}if you want to be victorious, you need to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们还有场仗要赢\N{\rYUANWEN}We have a war to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从明天开始\N{\rYUANWEN}It starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,山姆 去把麦克斯文先生叫来\N{\rYUANWEN}Sam, go fetch Mr. McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 布鲁尔先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir, Mr. Brewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,警长 有什么事吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我是来给你送东西的  -这是什么\N{\rYUANWEN}- I have something for you. - What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,针对这家店的法律令状\N{\rYUANWEN}It's a legal writ against this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们得即刻停业\N{\rYUANWEN}You're gonna have to close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这家商店不许再做生意\N{\rYUANWEN}This store is no longer trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们都得回家了\N{\rYUANWEN}You're all gonna have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:12.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 都解散吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Please go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不能这么做\N{\rYUANWEN}You can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这家店长期非法经营\N{\rYUANWEN}This store has been trading illegally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:19.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这得由法院说了算\N{\rYUANWEN}That's for the courts to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你非常清楚 我们会抗辩的\N{\rYUANWEN}And you known damn well we'll fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布鲁尔先生 你们没机会赢\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Brewer, you have no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,后续还会有针对汤斯顿先生\N{\rYUANWEN}And you can expect warrants
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和麦克斯文先生的搜查令\N{\rYUANWEN}from Mr. Tunstall and Mr. McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是副警长\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm a Deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不能就这样越过我\N{\rYUANWEN}You can't just go over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布鲁尔先生 你的副警长任命\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Brewer, your appointment as Deputy Sheriff
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,已被圣达菲的地方检察官托马斯·卡特伦\N{\rYUANWEN}has been rescinded, by order of District Attorney,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下令撤销\N{\rYUANWEN}Thomas Catron in Santa Fe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只能要求你交出警徽了\N{\rYUANWEN}And I'm obliged to ask you to surrender your badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这究竟怎么回事\N{\rYUANWEN}What in hell's name is happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您这是在干什么 警长\N{\rYUANWEN}What are you trying to do, Sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是送达令状 麦克斯文先生\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm only serving a Iegal writ, Mr. McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我职责所在\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm only trying to do my duty and nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们付了你多少钱\N{\rYUANWEN}How much did they pay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得告诉你 麦克斯文先生\N{\rYUANWEN}I got to tell you, Mr. McSween,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你也因严重犯罪被调查\N{\rYUANWEN}that you too are being investigated for serious crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我建议您注意言行举止\N{\rYUANWEN}So I suggest that you mind your manners,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小心祸从口出\N{\rYUANWEN}keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等等 等等\N{\rYUANWEN}Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我听说布雷迪警长会带着武装队\N{\rYUANWEN}So, I've heard that Sheriff Brady and a posse
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,于今早到达\N{\rYUANWEN}will arrive here in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为你下达令状 没收你的一切马匹\N{\rYUANWEN}to serve you with a writ and seize all of your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们完全不在乎这么做的合法性\N{\rYUANWEN}They don't give a hang about the legalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\rYUANWEN}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:15.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,迪克 你觉得我们该怎么办\N{\rYUANWEN}Dick, what do you think we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听你的 老板\N{\rYUANWEN}That's up to you, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们应该保卫这个牧场\N{\rYUANWEN}We should defend the ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,保卫你的财产\N{\rYUANWEN}Protect your property.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得跟他们硬刚\N{\rYUANWEN}We gotta fight'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利说得对\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们必须表明立场\N{\rYUANWEN}We have to take a stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你俩谁先行去趟林肯 告诉胡安\N{\rYUANWEN}One of you should ride into Lincoln and tell Juan Patron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:44.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤姆 去找查理和乔治\N{\rYUANWEN}Tom, go get Charlie and George.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把所有武器都拿来 快\N{\rYUANWEN}We need every gun we can get. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麦克斯文先生 你需要枪吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. McSween, would you like a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不需要\N{\rYUANWEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我做了这么多年牧师\N{\rYUANWEN}I was a pastor all these years
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我发过誓 再也不碰枪\N{\rYUANWEN}and I've sworn off ever using a gun myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你就先回家吧 亚历山大\N{\rYUANWEN}Then you best go home, Alexander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:02.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我们能应付得了  -我知道你们会的\N{\rYUANWEN}- We'll manage. - I know you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你\N{\rYUANWEN}God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有你\N{\rYUANWEN}And you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们把这些隔板堆在一起\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's stack these as barricades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,堵住大门\N{\rYUANWEN}Block the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\rYUANWEN}Outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,难以置信\N{\rYUANWEN}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谁输的筹码都没了\N{\rYUANWEN}Who's got no chips left?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是 在想事情\N{\rYUANWEN}I was just...thinking about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你如果执意要知道的话 我在\N{\rYUANWEN}If you really want to know, I was, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在想我父亲\N{\rYUANWEN}...thinking about my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是个怎样的人\N{\rYUANWEN}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯 他是个\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, he was a...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:28.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得他是那个阶级背景下的\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I suppose he was rather typical for an Englishman
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:29.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,典型英国人\N{\rYUANWEN}of his class and background.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:35.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,聪明至极 成功至极 还非常有原则\N{\rYUANWEN}Highly intelligent, highly principled, very successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他为我定的标准极高 高到可笑\N{\rYUANWEN}He set this absurdly high bar for me to achieve,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在我达不到时\N{\rYUANWEN}and then whenever I failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他会用尽办法骂我 罚我\N{\rYUANWEN}he found ways to scold and punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我总是拼命想求他认可\N{\rYUANWEN}I was always desperate to impress him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这也是我来这里打拼的原因\N{\rYUANWEN}That's why I came to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:59.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想创造属于我自己的东西\N{\rYUANWEN}I wanted to create something of my own
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:03.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能让我父亲为我骄傲的东西\N{\rYUANWEN}that would make my father at least proud of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得你已经做到了\N{\rYUANWEN}I think that's exactly what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可在我看来 我搞砸了一切\N{\rYUANWEN}Seems to me that I'm making rather a mess of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:17.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿先生 你敢于跟一群混蛋对峙\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Tunstall, you're up against some real mean motherfuckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:23.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我为你的勇气骄傲\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm proud of you for standing up to'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看看周围吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Just look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:30.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你身后站着这片土地上最优秀的人\N{\rYUANWEN}You got some of the best souls in the territory behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们诚实 善良\N{\rYUANWEN}Good, honest people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,仅凭这一点 你就成功了\N{\rYUANWEN}That alone tells me you're succeeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您父亲只要不疯不傻\N{\rYUANWEN}And if your father had any sense or understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他就会明白的\N{\rYUANWEN}he'd see that himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:00.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我这话你可能不爱听\N{\rYUANWEN}You are not going to want to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我不能拿这些人的生命冒险\N{\rYUANWEN}But I can't put the lives of all these people on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想眼看\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't want to see
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:10.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这么多正义之士因我被杀\N{\rYUANWEN}all these honest and decent folk getting killed in my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想决一死战 至少现在不想\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't want a showdown. Not yet, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可你说过我们得面对他们\N{\rYUANWEN}You said we had to stand up to'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说过我们别无选择\N{\rYUANWEN}You said we didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许我们有的选\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, maybe we do have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我刚在想 也许我们可以在警长来之前\N{\rYUANWEN}I was just thinking that we could move
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把马匹转移到别处\N{\rYUANWEN}the horses before the sheriff gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在堡垒附近另买了一个农场\N{\rYUANWEN}I bought another farm up near the fort
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可以把人马带到那里 从长计议\N{\rYUANWEN}and we can take them there and then figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:30.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得警长不会来追\N{\rYUANWEN}the next step and I don't think the sheriff will follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 我们不能总是逃避\N{\rYUANWEN}No, we can't keep runnin'away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:40.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得我是脓包 是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You think I'm being a coward, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:49.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想让你和这些人为我送命\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't want you or any of these people to die for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会无法面对自己\N{\rYUANWEN}I couldn't live with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:59.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我情愿你们觉得我是脓包\N{\rYUANWEN}Now if that makes me a coward, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,快点吧\N{\rYUANWEN}－ Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得赶在武装队之前离开\N{\rYUANWEN}We gotta clear out before the posse gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿先生觉得警长不会来追\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Tunstall thinks the sheriff won't try and follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:43.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我不敢肯定\N{\rYUANWEN}But I ain't so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:45.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们俩轮流垫后 保持警惕\N{\rYUANWEN}You two take it in turns to drop back and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 你父亲呢\N{\rYUANWEN}So, what about your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是个什么样的人\N{\rYUANWEN}What kind of a man was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是个骄傲的爱尔兰人\N{\rYUANWEN}He was a proud Irishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他从未想过背井离乡\N{\rYUANWEN}He never wanted to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,尽管那里已经没什么值得他留恋的了\N{\rYUANWEN}There just wasn't much left for him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:29.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事实证明 纽约也不适合移民居住\N{\rYUANWEN}Turns out there wasn't much for immigrants in New York either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-所以你是穷人咯  -非常穷\N{\rYUANWEN}So, you were poor? - Oh, dirt poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我父母才决定西行\N{\rYUANWEN}That's why my parents decided to come out west.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想过上更好的生活\N{\rYUANWEN}To find a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一定很难吧\N{\rYUANWEN}It must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马车行进的路上 我父亲生病了\N{\rYUANWEN}Somewhere along the wagon trail, my father got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他失去了求生意志\N{\rYUANWEN}He kinda gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:02.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你爱你父亲吗 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you love him, Billy? Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他虽然是我父亲\N{\rYUANWEN}He was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但却放弃了我\N{\rYUANWEN}But he quit on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我发誓 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}I swear to you, Billy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不会让你失望的\N{\rYUANWEN}I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们不在这 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}They're not here, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行了 我又不瞎\N{\rYUANWEN}AII right! You think I can't see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,追上他们 小伙子们\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's follow'em, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们不该那么做\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't think we should do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为啥\N{\rYUANWEN}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们只是布雷迪的武装队\N{\rYUANWEN}We're just Brady's posse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从法律上讲 我们要做的就是\N{\rYUANWEN}Legally, all we're supposed to do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给汤斯顿送达传票 抓几匹马走\N{\rYUANWEN}is serve Tunstall a writ, seize some horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而不是追着他走过半个国家\N{\rYUANWEN}Not chase him halfway across the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们就他妈是法律\N{\rYUANWEN}We are the fuckin' law!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我们想干什么就干什么  -杰西说的对\N{\rYUANWEN}- We do what we want, boys. - Jesse's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是这么跟我们说的 我们也就该这么做\N{\rYUANWEN}That's what we've been told. That's what we outta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是个坏主意\N{\rYUANWEN}It's a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得跟警长说声\N{\rYUANWEN}We gotta talk to the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们是有什么毛病\N{\rYUANWEN}What is wrong with all of ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们都知道来这到底该做什么\N{\rYUANWEN}We all know what we are really meant to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跟你们说 我的刀已磨光\N{\rYUANWEN}I tell you, my knife is sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就等着杀人剥皮了\N{\rYUANWEN}and I feel like scalping someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以赶紧跟我去追他们吧 小伙子们\N{\rYUANWEN}So, let's get after em, boys! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,驾 驾\N{\rYUANWEN}Hiya! Hiya! Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西 这些痕迹看上去是新的\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse, these tracks look fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有人跟踪吗 乔治\N{\rYUANWEN}Anyone following, George?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有 一个人影都看不到\N{\rYUANWEN}No. AII clear. Didn't see a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:02.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}AII right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们饿了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You boys hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,饿了 看到午餐了 走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, and there's our lunch. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去吧比利 你可是神枪手\N{\rYUANWEN}Go on, Billy. You're the best marksman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去给咱们抓午餐吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Go get us some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走了 汤姆\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小心点马 汤斯顿先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mind the horses, Mr. Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,觉得今天有的吃吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Think we gonna eat today? -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果他们真能打中什么的话\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe if they can actually hit anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,靠\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah, shitl
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是杰西和他手下\N{\rYUANWEN}It's Jesse and his boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他要去哪\N{\rYUANWEN}Where's he goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,驾\N{\rYUANWEN}Hiya! Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:45.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早了 汤斯顿先生落单了\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah shit. That's Tunstall. He's on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我这就去救他 在这等我\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm gonna go get him. Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真不该留下他一人的\N{\rYUANWEN}- - I shouldn't have left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不该丢下他一人\N{\rYUANWEN}I shouldn't have left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rYUANWEN}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,草\N{\rYUANWEN}Fuck! -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,草\N{\rYUANWEN}Fuck! -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如何\N{\rYUANWEN}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:41.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,黎明时分 他们带着马从汤斯顿的牧场出发\N{\rYUANWEN}They struck out from Tunstall's ranch around dawn, with horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:46.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们寻迹跟上了他们 抓了个正着\N{\rYUANWEN}Picked up their trail, and we caught up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:47.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\rYUANWEN}And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后发生了火拼\N{\rYUANWEN}And there was a firefight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们有合法权力来扣押这些马匹\N{\rYUANWEN}Now we had legal authority to seize those animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但他们却进行了抵抗\N{\rYUANWEN}but they were bent on resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们担心自己的生命安全\N{\rYUANWEN}We were afraid for our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,终于 我们见到了汤斯顿本人\N{\rYUANWEN}Finally, we tracked down Tunstall himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:04.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们让他投降 但他拒绝了\N{\rYUANWEN}We told him to surrender, but he just refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:06.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他朝我们开枪 我们反击\N{\rYUANWEN}He fired at us, and we fired back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:08.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说他死了\N{\rYUANWEN}And you're saying he's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:12.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:15.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拒捕吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Resisting arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:17.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:23.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你他妈觉得这事哪里好笑\N{\rYUANWEN}In what fucking universe do you find this amusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:25.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你做的事会给我们所有人\N{\rYUANWEN}What you've done may have terrible consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都招来恶果\N{\rYUANWEN}for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以别他妈跟我笑嘻嘻的\N{\rYUANWEN}So don't look so fucking happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:13.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你给了我希望\N{\rYUANWEN}You gave me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:18.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个新生活\N{\rYUANWEN}A new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:38.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我以我已逝的母亲起誓\N{\rYUANWEN}I swear on my mother's grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:43.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会杀掉所有害死你的人\N{\rYUANWEN}...I will kill every man involved in your murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:48.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,付出生命也在所不惜 所以上帝请你帮我\N{\rYUANWEN}or die myself in the attempt, so help me God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:08.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们终于弄死了那个混蛋\N{\rYUANWEN}We finally got the fucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:17.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,圣诞他妈的快乐 所有人\N{\rYUANWEN}Happy fucking Christmas, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:24.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen! Ho- ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:27.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听我说一句 小伙子们 注意了\N{\rYUANWEN}Listen up, boys. Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:34.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,今天是浩世的大日子\N{\rYUANWEN}Today is a great day for the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:41.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我建议敬创始人\N{\rYUANWEN}And that is why I want to salute the founder
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.29,0:24:44.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,战争英雄墨菲上校一杯\N{\rYUANWEN}Major Murphy, a war hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.54,0:24:46.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,敬墨菲上校\N{\rYUANWEN}To Major Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.04,0:24:50.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨菲上校 墨菲上校\N{\rYUANWEN}Major Murphy! Major Murphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.09,0:24:57.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来点音乐啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Where's the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.92,0:25:33.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Howdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.63,0:25:35.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你来这有什么事吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What's your business here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.43,0:25:39.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要跟浩世的莱利先生开会\N{\rYUANWEN}I have a meeting with Mr. Riley at the House,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.68,0:25:41.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不知道这事跟你有啥关系\N{\rYUANWEN}if it's any of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.60,0:25:46.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你叫什么  -埃德加·沃尔兹\N{\rYUANWEN}- What's your name? - My name's Edgar Walz.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.35,0:25:49.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是托马斯·卡特伦的代表律师\N{\rYUANWEN}I represent Thomas Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:54.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我听说过他\N{\rYUANWEN}I heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.61,0:25:57.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你又是谁呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.45,0:25:59.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西·埃文斯\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm Jesse Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.83,0:26:04.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,久闻大名啊\N{\rYUANWEN}I've heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.54,0:26:08.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们告诉我说你是个危险人物\N{\rYUANWEN}They, um, they tell me you're a dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.38,0:26:12.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我喜欢\N{\rYUANWEN}I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.46,0:26:18.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯 那要看你怎么理解危险了 沃尔兹先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, well, depends on what you mean by dangerous, Mr. Walz.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.13,0:26:21.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 我今后可能用得着你\N{\rYUANWEN}What I mean is I might have a use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.14,0:26:23.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许在未来的某个时候\N{\rYUANWEN}In due course.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.56,0:26:28.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你 埃文斯先生\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm glad we met, Mr. Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.73,0:26:30.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,叫我杰西就行\N{\rYUANWEN}Call me Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.65,0:26:33.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可真友善\N{\rYUANWEN}That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.82,0:26:35.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Now Jesse...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.32,0:26:38.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能过了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}May I pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.66,0:26:41.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\rYUANWEN}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.26,0:26:56.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,王八蛋\N{\rYUANWEN}Prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.89,0:27:02.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\rYUANWEN}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.51,0:27:06.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是来通知你 卡特伦先生\N{\rYUANWEN}I came to inform you that Mr. Catron is very pleased
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.02,0:27:10.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对约翰·汤斯顿不再参与林肯县经济事务一事\N{\rYUANWEN}with the termination of John Tunstall's interest
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.73,0:27:13.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,深感高兴\N{\rYUANWEN}in the economic affairs of Lincoln County.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.44,0:27:14.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.90,0:27:16.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没人想看到这样的结果\N{\rYUANWEN}It's something that no one wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.36,0:27:19.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但汤斯顿先生毕竟犯了法\N{\rYUANWEN}but the fact remains that Tunstall was a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.61,0:27:21.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真是让人难过啊\N{\rYUANWEN}It's all been very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.95,0:27:23.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是我还是要提醒你\N{\rYUANWEN}However, I must remind you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.87,0:27:27.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还欠卡特伦先生一大笔债\N{\rYUANWEN}that you are still in substantial debt to Mr. Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.20,0:27:31.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且卡特伦先生对目前的情况还是不满意\N{\rYUANWEN}And Mr. Catron remains unhappy with the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.42,0:27:34.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.29,0:27:37.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿不挡路了 情况就完全改变了啊\N{\rYUANWEN}With Tunstall outta the way, things have completely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.21,0:27:40.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是觉得我傻吗 莱利先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you take me for a fool, Mr. Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.43,0:27:43.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马上就要开战了\N{\rYUANWEN}There's a serious war going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.76,0:27:45.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦先生非常担心\N{\rYUANWEN}and Mr. Catron is very concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.56,0:27:48.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}that this, um, Billy the Kid can,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.22,0:27:49.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,靠他一人就能给你的生意和手下\N{\rYUANWEN}on his own account, inflict serious damage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.98,0:27:51.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,造成重创\N{\rYUANWEN}on your business and employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.94,0:27:53.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可以处理\N{\rYUANWEN}We can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.73,0:27:55.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们有枪\N{\rYUANWEN}We've got the guns
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.27,0:27:57.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且浩世也是个大机构\N{\rYUANWEN}and the House is a fuckin' institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.07,0:27:59.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且我觉得是时候\N{\rYUANWEN}And I think it's about time
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.65,0:28:02.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你表现出一点尊敬了 沃尔兹先生\N{\rYUANWEN}that you start respecting that, Mr. Walz.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.91,0:28:06.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想知道我怎么看的吗 莱利\N{\rYUANWEN}Wanna know how I see it, Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.66,0:28:13.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,浩世即将面临严重的财务危机\N{\rYUANWEN}The House is facing imminent financial disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.92,0:28:16.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,鉴于情况危急\N{\rYUANWEN}So, in view of this perilous situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.96,0:28:19.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦先生建议你将\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Catron is suggesting that you mortgage to him
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.26,0:28:22.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯县的所有股份抵押给他\N{\rYUANWEN}all your holdings in Lincoln County.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.30,0:28:26.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为回报卡特伦先生会借给你25000美元\N{\rYUANWEN}In return, Mr. Catron will lend you 25, 000 dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.76,0:28:29.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,三个月内偿还即可\N{\rYUANWEN}repayable in three months'time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.98,0:28:34.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你拖欠贷款\N{\rYUANWEN}If you default on the loan, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:36.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦先生将拥有所有抵押财产\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Catron will own all mortgaged property.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.65,0:28:41.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我以为我们是在合伙做生意\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought that we were in business together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.36,0:28:43.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莱利先生 你不会不知道吧 在所有商业交易中\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Riley, don't you know that in all business transactions
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.99,0:28:45.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都有一个主导的合伙人\N{\rYUANWEN}there is one leading partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.83,0:28:50.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我他妈上哪去弄这笔钱\N{\rYUANWEN}How the fuck am I supposed to find this money?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.45,0:28:52.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是你的事了\N{\rYUANWEN}That's your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.96,0:28:55.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我建议你尽快\N{\rYUANWEN}But I suggest you bring an end to this war
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.46,0:28:56.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,结束这场战斗\N{\rYUANWEN}as promptly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.96,0:28:58.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来吧 莱利先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Come, come, Mr. Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.71,0:29:00.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我之前就说过 在商言商\N{\rYUANWEN}I've told you before, this is business.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.63,0:29:02.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,生意里可容不下你的多愁善感\N{\rYUANWEN}There's no sentiment in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.05,0:29:08.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在 如果你接受这个抵押协议\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, if you accept the terms of this mortgage agreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.51,0:29:11.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请在这份具有法律效力的文件上签字吧\N{\rYUANWEN}please sign this legal and binding document.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.73,0:29:22.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,非常好\N{\rYUANWEN}Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.16,0:29:35.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很荣幸跟您合作\N{\rYUANWEN}Been a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.68,0:29:47.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就不用送了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll see myself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.69,0:30:00.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这结果你没想到吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What'd you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.11,0:30:05.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我很久以前就跟你说过\N{\rYUANWEN}I told you a long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.40,0:30:08.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟卡特伦这种人合作就是你太天真了\N{\rYUANWEN}you are too naive be dealing with a man like Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.45,0:30:11.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他可比你精明多了\N{\rYUANWEN}He's smarter than you'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.62,0:30:17.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不用愚蠢酒鬼给我什么狗屁建议\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't need any fuckin'advice from a stupid old drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.88,0:30:23.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不会开枪的\N{\rYUANWEN}You won't shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:30.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你一开枪就什么都没有了 莱利\N{\rYUANWEN}The minute you shoot me, Riley, you lose everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.39,0:30:32.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好好想想吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.10,0:30:36.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是唯一能跟卡特伦说上话的人\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm the only person that can talk to Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.27,0:30:38.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他也只会听我的\N{\rYUANWEN}And I'm the only person he'll listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.33,0:30:55.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来吧 开枪啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Go on, shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.96,0:30:59.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你他妈开枪啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Fuckin'shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.92,0:31:07.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦 愿你把我藏在阴间\N{\rYUANWEN}O that thou wouldest hide me in the grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.47,0:31:10.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,愿你把我隐瞒\N{\rYUANWEN}that thou wouldest keep me secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.84,0:31:12.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等你的忿怒过去\N{\rYUANWEN}until thy wrath be past,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.68,0:31:16.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,愿你为我定一个日期 记念我\N{\rYUANWEN}that thou wouldest appoint me a set time, and remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.77,0:31:19.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,人死了岂能再活呢\N{\rYUANWEN}If a man die, shall he live again?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.98,0:31:22.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只要在我一切争战的日子等候\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI the days of my appointed time will I wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.61,0:31:24.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等我被改变\N{\rYUANWEN}- till my change come. -
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.44,0:31:27.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你呼唤 我就回答你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thou shalt call, and I will answer thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.11,0:31:27.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你必切望自己手所做的工\N{\rYUANWEN}Thou wilt have a desire to the work
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.74,0:31:28.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你必切望自己手所做的工\N{\rYUANWEN}Thou wilt have a desire to the work
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.82,0:31:29.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恶人的计算\N{\rYUANWEN}of thine hands. For now thou numberest my steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.90,0:31:32.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恶人的计算\N{\rYUANWEN}of thine hands. For now thou numberest my steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.12,0:31:34.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你也必顾念\N{\rYUANWEN}Dost thou not watch over my sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.53,0:31:36.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的过犯被封在囊中\N{\rYUANWEN}My transgression is sealed up in a bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.04,0:31:39.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你缝补了我的罪孽\N{\rYUANWEN}and thou sewest up mine iniquity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.29,0:31:42.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,山崩必归于无有\N{\rYUANWEN}And surely the mountains falling cometh to nought,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.13,0:31:43.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,磐石必因所挪开而不在原处\N{\rYUANWEN}and the rock is removed...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.55,0:31:48.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们 请安静\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen, please, let's have some order!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.05,0:31:51.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.85,0:31:55.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我必须指出 我们的首要任务\N{\rYUANWEN}I have to tell you that our first duty
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.68,0:31:57.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是要找出一个合法方案\N{\rYUANWEN}is to try and find a legal solution,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.52,0:31:59.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而不是自行执法\N{\rYUANWEN}rather than take the law into our own hands.
