Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.82,0:32:08.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,涉嫌共谋杀害约翰·汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}with complicity in the murder of John Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.82,0:32:11.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我还会要求将汤斯顿的产业\N{\rYUANWEN}I will also demand the return of Tunstall's store
