Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.82,0:32:14.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麦克斯文先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. McSween!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.41,0:32:18.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我理解你对程序正义的尊重\N{\rYUANWEN}I understand your faith in the due process of the law,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.70,0:32:20.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我不能共席\N{\rYUANWEN}but I do not share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.66,0:32:23.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这在林肯县不存在 在新墨西哥不存在\N{\rYUANWEN}Not here in Lincoln. Not in New Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.09,0:32:29.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家都很清楚 布雷迪警长\N{\rYUANWEN}It is clear to all of us that Sheriff Brady,
