Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.67,0:32:32.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,包括其他议员都是一丘之貉\N{\rYUANWEN}and all the other lawmakers are corrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.93,0:32:35.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们不配我们信任\N{\rYUANWEN}and no longer deserve our trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.26,0:32:38.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 我祈求你 我们需要法律的支持\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy, I beg you. We need the law on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.22,0:32:41.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,法律 麦克斯文 这里没有法律\N{\rYUANWEN}What law, McSween? There is no law.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.39,0:32:43.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只有我们\N{\rYUANWEN}It is just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.19,0:32:45.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们决定订立誓约\N{\rYUANWEN}And what we're decided upon is a pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.69,0:32:48.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,组建一支部队 跟浩世开战\N{\rYUANWEN}to form a fighting force, to take this war to the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.03,0:32:52.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们应该自称监管者\N{\rYUANWEN}And we should call ourselves the Regulators.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.57,0:32:54.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们苦枉法之徒久矣\N{\rYUANWEN}That's those who assemble to regulate
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.57,0:32:58.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以团结在一起进行监管和纠正\N{\rYUANWEN}or set to right an intolerable or illegal situation.
