Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.29,0:33:07.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是时候了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now's the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.05,0:33:11.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.30,0:33:19.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会带领大家 我们会拼尽全力\N{\rYUANWEN}I'|I lead you and we'll fight like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.47,0:33:22.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我不想做的事 绝不会逼大家上前\N{\rYUANWEN}But I will not ask you to do anything I wouldn't do myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.31,0:33:28.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家同进同退 这是唯一的办法了\N{\rYUANWEN}We're in this together. It's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.94,0:33:31.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我明白大家的决定\N{\rYUANWEN}I understand what's been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.07,0:33:34.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我理解个中原因\N{\rYUANWEN}And, and I can understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.11,0:33:38.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我希望大家明白 用暴力\N{\rYUANWEN}But I want you all to appreciate that if you respond
