Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.08,0:33:44.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,将会走上一条不归路\N{\rYUANWEN}there will be no turning back,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.16,0:33:47.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,会让这里哀鸿遍野\N{\rYUANWEN}and there will be a lot of bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.25,0:33:52.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就哀鸿遍野吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Then let there be bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.87,0:34:20.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Gracias.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.79,0:34:30.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.17,0:34:33.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我刚听说汤斯顿先生的事\N{\rYUANWEN}I just heard about Senor Tunstall.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.67,0:34:38.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 我知道他对你很重要\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm so sorry. I know what he meant to you.
