Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.57,0:34:55.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,挺好的 谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.01,0:35:23.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}What is it?
