Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.95,0:35:40.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.28,0:35:45.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我所向往的生活 祈求的未来\N{\rYUANWEN}The life I'd hoped for, the future I pray for,
