Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.70,0:35:49.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\rYUANWEN}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.92,0:35:53.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我\N{\rYUANWEN}I.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.38,0:35:56.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得手刃汤斯顿的仇人\N{\rYUANWEN}I have to kill the men who murdered Tunstall.
