Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.47,0:36:02.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,警察会逮捕他们 把他们进监绞死的\N{\rYUANWEN}They will be arrested. Put in jail. Hanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.59,0:36:03.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在这里不会\N{\rYUANWEN}Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.89,0:36:06.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这里没有法律可言\N{\rYUANWEN}There's no Iaw here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.39,0:36:10.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想要正义 就得把王法掌握在自己手中\N{\rYUANWEN}If I want justice, I have to take the law into my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.98,0:36:12.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这么说你又要当逃犯了\N{\rYUANWEN}So, you'd be an outlaw again?
