Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.90,0:36:16.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你活着一天 就一天不得安宁\N{\rYUANWEN}Even if you live, you won't have any peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.73,0:36:18.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过着逃亡的日子 这就是你想要的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}they'll hunt you down. Is that what you want?
