Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.49,0:37:53.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-是谁  -我是汤姆·欧费亚德\N{\rYUANWEN}- Who's that? - My name's Tom O'Folliard.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.00,0:37:55.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有消息你一定想听\N{\rYUANWEN}I've got some news you might wanna hear
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.71,0:37:57.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-跟比利小子有关  -什么消息\N{\rYUANWEN}- about Billy the Kid. - What kind of news?
