Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.72,0:38:07.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 我不开枪\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I ain't gonna shoot ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.43,0:38:12.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你要说什么\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell me what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.02,0:38:19.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别他妈出声 不然你就死定了\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't make a fuckin' noise or you're dead.
