Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.73,0:38:24.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘘 别出声\N{\rYUANWEN}Shh. Shush now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.95,0:38:27.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想伤害你 贝克维斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, I don't want to hurt you, Beckwith.
