Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.75,0:39:22.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我拿到名字了\N{\rYUANWEN}Got the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.67,0:39:25.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杀害汤斯顿的人\N{\rYUANWEN}The ones who killed Tunstall.
