Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.93,0:39:34.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.97,0:39:36.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,贝克维斯说没有\N{\rYUANWEN}Beckwith says not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.35,0:39:40.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们先等等 看看麦克斯文从法庭带来的消息\N{\rYUANWEN}First, we see if McSween has made any progress in the courts.
