Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.19,0:43:50.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.27,0:43:54.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莫顿和贝克\N{\rYUANWEN}Morton and Baker!
