Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.79,0:44:11.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利不会让我们走的\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy's not gonna let us walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.29,0:44:13.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\rYUANWEN}You have my word.
